sentences.sentence: Dieter Vandoren has been working on the integration project series for several years.

sentences.sentence: A few are no-brainers and other will surprise even the most seasoned dieter.

sentences.sentence: Now that I'm now no longer a dieter, I might as well have another cookie.
sentences.translation: 现在我已经不再减肥了，再吃一块饼干没什么了不起的。
